1
00:01:35,180 --> 00:01:36,510
<i>[Scarlet Heart 2]</i>

2
00:01:36,510 --> 00:01:43,020
<i>[Episode 21]</i>

3
00:01:46,646 --> 00:01:48,587
I'm getting a phone call.

4
00:01:50,854 --> 00:01:53,504
He's here. I'll go pick him up.

5
00:01:58,479 --> 00:01:59,871
What?

6
00:02:02,062 --> 00:02:05,095
Fine, go do your thing.

7
00:02:16,019 --> 00:02:17,787
What's wrong?

8
00:02:17,787 --> 00:02:19,896
He said he suddenly has a meeting.

9
00:02:19,896 --> 00:02:21,712
He can't make it.

10
00:02:22,938 --> 00:02:25,671
There will be plenty of opportunities.

11
00:02:26,854 --> 00:02:28,354
You're right.

12
00:02:28,354 --> 00:02:31,896
Happy women need their alone time too.

13
00:02:31,896 --> 00:02:37,320
Let's party tonight!

14
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:44,062
♪ Unfortunately, you're not with me until the very end ♪

15
00:02:44,062 --> 00:02:46,512
You're off-key.

16
00:02:48,145 --> 00:02:52,329
Princess, do you remember when I broke up with my boyfriend in college?

17
00:02:52,329 --> 00:02:53,712
We also sang this song.

18
00:02:53,712 --> 00:02:55,603
Really?

19
00:02:56,395 --> 00:02:58,554
I don't remember.

20
00:02:59,337 --> 00:03:03,671
I didn't realize until now.

21
00:03:03,671 --> 00:03:05,854
I think you got chubbier.

22
00:03:05,854 --> 00:03:09,270
Really? It might be edema.

23
00:03:09,270 --> 00:03:12,103
Plus, I still haven't adjusted to the time difference.

24
00:03:12,103 --> 00:03:14,354
Then you need to go to bed early tonight.

25
00:03:14,354 --> 00:03:15,471
No way.

26
00:03:15,471 --> 00:03:18,437
I can't sleep if I'm hanging out with you.

27
00:03:18,437 --> 00:03:21,938
I have many things to tell you.

28
00:03:21,938 --> 00:03:23,203
Piggy.

29
00:03:23,203 --> 00:03:24,562
You know,

30
00:03:24,562 --> 00:03:29,770
I'm treating today as my bachelorette party.

31
00:03:30,838 --> 00:03:32,604
You're getting married?

32
00:03:32,604 --> 00:03:35,771
I'm getting married in spirit.

33
00:03:36,395 --> 00:03:37,712
After today,

34
00:03:37,712 --> 00:03:41,879
I will be the woman who backs a successful man.

35
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:44,287
Married in spirit?

36
00:03:45,062 --> 00:03:46,854
I don't understand.

37
00:03:47,687 --> 00:03:50,145
You don't get it.

38
00:03:50,145 --> 00:03:53,979
Because you haven't met your Mr. Right.

39
00:03:53,979 --> 00:03:55,403
Yes I have.

40
00:03:55,403 --> 00:03:58,229
Black Cat Detective is my Mr. Right.

41
00:03:59,187 --> 00:04:02,020
You couldn't meet my boyfriend today.

42
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:04,295
You should go see your Black Cat Detective.

43
00:04:04,295 --> 00:04:05,629
No way.

44
00:04:05,629 --> 00:04:08,871
I don't want him to see me like this.

45
00:04:09,629 --> 00:04:14,203
I'm extra different today.

46
00:04:14,203 --> 00:04:16,879
I never had so much to drink before.

47
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:24,487
My boyfriend.

48
00:04:25,395 --> 00:04:27,379
Why did he go away?

49
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:32,062
He sure is your secret boyfriend.

50
00:04:32,062 --> 00:04:33,019
But...

51
00:04:33,019 --> 00:04:37,804
He must be famous if he's appearing on this street. Who is he?

52
00:04:38,796 --> 00:04:40,395
I'm not telling you.

53
00:04:40,395 --> 00:04:44,020
I want to keep him a secret.

54
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:45,771
How could you do this to me?

55
00:04:45,771 --> 00:04:47,338
Of course.

56
00:04:47,338 --> 00:04:51,229
I want you to be surprised.

57
00:04:51,229 --> 00:04:53,662
I want you to be jealous!

58
00:04:53,662 --> 00:04:57,762
I'm gonna get you!

59
00:05:11,129 --> 00:05:12,879
Don't run.

60
00:05:17,819 --> 00:05:21,320
Let me see what we have to eat tonight.

61
00:05:22,596 --> 00:05:24,254
The answer is...

62
00:05:24,254 --> 00:05:26,070
Two packs of udon,

63
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:28,487
three tomatoes, one apple,

64
00:05:28,487 --> 00:05:30,362
milk and eggs.

65
00:05:30,362 --> 00:05:31,696
Nothing else.

66
00:05:31,696 --> 00:05:33,429
That's it?

67
00:05:33,429 --> 00:05:36,154
We shouldn't have such oily food at night.

68
00:05:36,154 --> 00:05:41,246
Do you want a bowl of tomato egg udon noodle soup?

69
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:44,738
Do you not want to make it?

70
00:05:44,738 --> 00:05:46,645
Fine, I don't want to eat anymore.

71
00:05:56,903 --> 00:05:58,903
Princess, don't be mad.

72
00:05:58,903 --> 00:06:01,712
I will make you something else.

73
00:06:01,712 --> 00:06:02,571
No.

74
00:06:02,571 --> 00:06:04,629
Give me ten minutes.

75
00:06:04,629 --> 00:06:08,129
I will make you tuna egg salad.

76
00:06:08,129 --> 00:06:10,029
What are you saying?

77
00:06:10,029 --> 00:06:12,379
Tuna egg salad.

78
00:06:15,045 --> 00:06:19,037
Then can I also add what you just said?

79
00:06:19,037 --> 00:06:21,420
The udon noodle soup?

80
00:06:22,254 --> 00:06:24,529
Can you finish that much food?

81
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:27,312
Fine.

82
00:06:27,312 --> 00:06:30,929
Please wait a moment.

83
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:34,117
Go!

84
00:06:42,632 --> 00:06:46,424
You made such a simple dish look so fancy.

85
00:06:46,424 --> 00:06:48,965
They look beautiful.

86
00:06:48,965 --> 00:06:51,739
I'm taking a picture for my mom.

87
00:06:51,739 --> 00:06:53,382
You're exaggerating.

88
00:06:53,382 --> 00:06:55,049
Auntie has seen it all.

89
00:06:55,049 --> 00:06:56,382
This is different.

90
00:06:56,382 --> 00:07:00,982
You were already such a great cook in college.

91
00:07:09,816 --> 00:07:11,274
Piggy.

92
00:07:11,274 --> 00:07:13,466
Your skills have improved.

93
00:07:13,466 --> 00:07:14,839
I'm glad you like it.

94
00:07:14,839 --> 00:07:16,758
I'll have more ingredients next time.

95
00:07:16,758 --> 00:07:18,765
Then we can have an abundant meal.

96
00:07:19,582 --> 00:07:23,340
It would be great if we could include your Black Cat Detective and my secret boyfriend.

97
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:25,090
The four of us should have a meal together.

98
00:07:25,132 --> 00:07:25,799
Okay.

99
00:07:25,799 --> 00:07:27,882
Make sure to help me in the kitchen.

100
00:07:27,882 --> 00:07:31,316
Deal.

101
00:07:35,649 --> 00:07:37,632
Are you getting tired?

102
00:07:37,632 --> 00:07:40,374
No, I'm fine.

103
00:07:40,374 --> 00:07:43,965
We'll talk all night then.

104
00:07:43,965 --> 00:07:45,758
No problem.

105
00:07:45,758 --> 00:07:46,474
Finish your food first.

106
00:07:46,474 --> 00:07:47,807
Okay.

107
00:08:12,923 --> 00:08:14,382
Don't move.

108
00:08:19,591 --> 00:08:21,778
Why are you drawing me?

109
00:08:21,778 --> 00:08:23,402
I forgot to tell you.

110
00:08:23,402 --> 00:08:24,943
I'm having an art exhibition.

111
00:08:24,943 --> 00:08:28,527
I'm showcasing all my work from the past few years.

112
00:08:28,527 --> 00:08:32,235
Don't tell me you're showcasing this drawing too.

113
00:08:32,235 --> 00:08:33,469
Of course.

114
00:08:33,469 --> 00:08:34,860
You are my best friend.

115
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:37,010
I have to put you up.

116
00:08:39,778 --> 00:08:43,360
Do you have a venue and time planned yet?

117
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:47,069
I'll try to go and support.

118
00:08:47,069 --> 00:08:51,210
I'll let you know after I settle something more important than this.

119
00:08:51,959 --> 00:08:54,569
Something more important than your art exhibition?

120
00:08:54,569 --> 00:08:55,977
What is it?

121
00:08:57,486 --> 00:08:58,960
Piggy.

122
00:08:59,736 --> 00:09:01,919
Have you ever thought about getting married?

123
00:09:03,002 --> 00:09:04,859
With Black Cat Detective?

124
00:09:05,719 --> 00:09:07,636
Of course.

125
00:09:09,027 --> 00:09:12,860
We just started dating, so I never really thought about it.

126
00:09:14,277 --> 00:09:17,727
What did you mean when you said you were getting married in spirit?

127
00:09:18,569 --> 00:09:23,144
It means I'm changing myself for the sake of getting married.

128
00:09:23,694 --> 00:09:26,860
Changing yourself for a man?

129
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:28,611
Is he really that great?

130
00:09:28,611 --> 00:09:31,640
He's worth it.

131
00:09:33,027 --> 00:09:36,377
I originally didn't think he was that great.

132
00:09:36,377 --> 00:09:38,290
But later on,

133
00:09:38,290 --> 00:09:41,190
I couldn't find anyone better than him.

134
00:09:42,902 --> 00:09:46,860
I'm getting more curious about your secret boyfriend.

135
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:49,669
You're so loyal to him.

136
00:09:49,669 --> 00:09:51,186
He must be amazing.

137
00:09:52,652 --> 00:09:56,319
I was spoiled child.

138
00:09:56,319 --> 00:09:58,902
I only cared about my own feelings.

139
00:09:58,902 --> 00:10:01,260
I never thought about how he felt.

140
00:10:01,260 --> 00:10:03,819
But when we weren't together anymore,

141
00:10:03,819 --> 00:10:07,819
I only then realized how good he was to me.

142
00:10:08,636 --> 00:10:12,260
So I'm determined to marry him.

143
00:10:12,260 --> 00:10:14,135
Okay.

144
00:10:14,135 --> 00:10:18,110
You're lucky to have found someone you love.

145
00:10:18,110 --> 00:10:20,027
I am happy for you.

146
00:10:20,027 --> 00:10:23,085
Don't forget our promise.

147
00:10:23,859 --> 00:10:25,802
What promise?

148
00:10:25,802 --> 00:10:27,302
To be my bridesmaid.

149
00:10:27,302 --> 00:10:30,227
Come on, I won't break my promise.

150
00:10:31,569 --> 00:10:33,444
Are you done?

151
00:10:33,444 --> 00:10:35,019
Almost done.

152
00:10:35,636 --> 00:10:36,911
I want to see it.

153
00:10:45,344 --> 00:10:48,111
You made me look so good.

154
00:10:49,386 --> 00:10:52,360
You're good-looking to begin with.

155
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:55,885
You also have good qualities that I don't have.

156
00:10:55,885 --> 00:11:00,527
You're perfect to me.

157
00:11:00,527 --> 00:11:03,911
I'm going to grow wings if you keep flattering me.

158
00:11:06,736 --> 00:11:08,427
I feel so lucky.

159
00:11:08,427 --> 00:11:10,527
To have a great friend like you,

160
00:11:10,527 --> 00:11:14,036
and to get married to the man I love.

161
00:11:14,036 --> 00:11:15,986
I have no regrets.

162
00:11:17,319 --> 00:11:19,302
You're so sentimental.

163
00:11:19,302 --> 00:11:22,077
I'm not used to this.

164
00:11:23,135 --> 00:11:24,511
You're hugging me so tight.

165
00:11:24,511 --> 00:11:26,969
Let go of me.

166
00:11:28,110 --> 00:11:31,802
Fine, take the crab.

167
00:11:31,802 --> 00:11:34,427
I don't want that.

168
00:11:35,943 --> 00:11:38,860
Fine, you can keep hugging me.

169
00:11:38,860 --> 00:11:41,227
Don't try to get rid of me.

170
00:11:53,552 --> 00:11:55,885
Princess, your phone.

171
00:11:55,885 --> 00:11:58,210
Help me answer it.

172
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:01,110
Fine.

173
00:12:01,852 --> 00:12:05,710
I'll take advantage of him then.

174
00:12:05,710 --> 00:12:07,302
Hello?

175
00:12:07,302 --> 00:12:09,110
Give it back to me.

176
00:12:09,110 --> 00:12:10,450
Hello?

177
00:12:11,952 --> 00:12:14,885
Stop.

178
00:12:14,885 --> 00:12:18,052
I stayed with a friend yesterday.

179
00:12:18,611 --> 00:12:21,069
Okay, see you later.

180
00:12:21,069 --> 00:12:22,427
Bye.

181
00:12:23,736 --> 00:12:24,994
Wake up.

182
00:12:24,994 --> 00:12:26,594
- Come meet my boyfriend.
- No, I want to sleep.

183
00:12:26,594 --> 00:12:28,752
No, I want to sleep.

184
00:12:28,752 --> 00:12:31,152
You weren't tired when you were tickling me just now.

185
00:12:31,152 --> 00:12:32,878
Get up.

186
00:12:32,878 --> 00:12:37,678
Princess, I'm an office worker.

187
00:12:37,678 --> 00:12:40,759
I want to wake up naturally.

188
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:42,960
Let me sleep ten more minutes.

189
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,386
Ten minutes.

190
00:12:46,010 --> 00:12:47,402
Fine.

191
00:12:47,402 --> 00:12:49,194
If you want to find me,

192
00:12:49,194 --> 00:12:51,930
go to the restaurant opposite of the art studio.

193
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:53,636
Okay?

194
00:12:53,636 --> 00:12:56,027
Go, see you later.

195
00:12:58,402 --> 00:13:00,302
I'm taking the drawing.

196
00:13:09,859 --> 00:13:11,277
Xinyi.

197
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:13,902
Sorry to keep you waiting.

198
00:13:13,902 --> 00:13:16,330
It's fine. I just got here.

199
00:13:16,330 --> 00:13:17,690
Have a seat.

200
00:13:18,552 --> 00:13:21,736
I was late because I stopped by my house.

201
00:13:21,736 --> 00:13:23,319
Thank you.

202
00:13:24,694 --> 00:13:26,069
For what?

203
00:13:26,069 --> 00:13:29,040
We talked about this restaurant in London.

204
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:30,650
Do you remember?

205
00:13:33,819 --> 00:13:36,194
The first time we met.

206
00:13:36,194 --> 00:13:38,502
It was raining

207
00:13:38,502 --> 00:13:40,235
and we both forgot to bring an umbrella.

208
00:13:40,235 --> 00:13:42,694
So we continued to talk.

209
00:13:42,694 --> 00:13:47,486
Then you told me that you missed this restaurant a lot.

210
00:13:47,486 --> 00:13:49,177
Did you forget?

211
00:13:50,611 --> 00:13:52,794
I think so.

212
00:13:54,860 --> 00:13:56,511
Fine.

213
00:13:56,511 --> 00:13:58,885
I guess I thought too much of it.

214
00:14:00,969 --> 00:14:02,386
But it's fine.

215
00:14:02,386 --> 00:14:04,552
Everything is good when I'm eating with you.

216
00:14:04,552 --> 00:14:06,110
Have you ordered yet?

217
00:14:06,110 --> 00:14:07,802
No, you can do it.

218
00:14:07,802 --> 00:14:09,552
You should order.

219
00:14:09,552 --> 00:14:13,678
I have to learn to follow your tastes.

220
00:14:13,678 --> 00:14:16,610
So you can stop saying I have the temper of a princess.

221
00:14:17,611 --> 00:14:19,511
Fine, I'll order.

222
00:14:26,527 --> 00:14:29,985
Why are you back so soon?

223
00:14:29,985 --> 00:14:31,719
Because I missed you.

224
00:14:34,627 --> 00:14:36,027
What's wrong?

225
00:14:36,027 --> 00:14:38,960
Are you too busy at work?

226
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,860
I'm fine.

227
00:14:46,486 --> 00:14:47,902
You know what?

228
00:14:47,902 --> 00:14:49,678
My advisor got married.

229
00:14:49,678 --> 00:14:52,177
His wife is beautiful.

230
00:14:52,177 --> 00:14:55,294
I went to their wedding ceremony.

231
00:14:55,294 --> 00:14:58,827
The bride is almost forty years younger than him.

232
00:15:11,719 --> 00:15:14,777
Sihan, sorry.

233
00:15:15,511 --> 00:15:17,611
Why are you apologizing?

234
00:15:17,611 --> 00:15:20,494
I have many things to tell you.

235
00:15:45,843 --> 00:15:46,719
That's it.

236
00:15:46,719 --> 00:15:47,902
Okay, please wait.

237
00:15:47,902 --> 00:15:49,219
Thank you.

238
00:16:01,350 --> 00:16:02,186
Hello?

239
00:16:02,186 --> 00:16:04,902
Hello, Black Cat Detective? Have you eaten yet?

240
00:16:04,902 --> 00:16:06,535
I'm eating now.

241
00:16:07,235 --> 00:16:08,402
Fine.

242
00:16:08,402 --> 00:16:10,094
How about you?

243
00:16:10,094 --> 00:16:12,719
Don't worry about me.

244
00:16:12,719 --> 00:16:16,210
Are you free tonight?

245
00:16:16,210 --> 00:16:17,611
Yes.

246
00:16:17,611 --> 00:16:20,444
Then can you eat with me tonight?

247
00:16:20,444 --> 00:16:21,760
Yes.

248
00:16:23,177 --> 00:16:24,943
Bye.

249
00:16:24,943 --> 00:16:26,394
Sorry.

250
00:16:27,902 --> 00:16:33,860
A phone call asking to meet for dinner at this is normally from a mother or a wife.

251
00:16:33,860 --> 00:16:37,859
But neither can be the case for you.

252
00:16:37,859 --> 00:16:40,002
Who called?

253
00:16:44,110 --> 00:16:47,277
Xinyi,

254
00:16:47,277 --> 00:16:50,544
if I told you that my new girlfriend just called,

255
00:16:50,544 --> 00:16:52,302
would you believe me?

256
00:16:53,252 --> 00:16:55,027
That's impossible.

257
00:16:55,027 --> 00:16:58,527
I would believe it if it were someone else sitting in front of me.

258
00:16:58,527 --> 00:17:02,210
But not you.

259
00:17:02,210 --> 00:17:03,902
Why not?

260
00:17:03,902 --> 00:17:08,177
Because you once told me it takes you a year to fall in love with someone.

261
00:17:08,177 --> 00:17:10,177
I didn't believe it at first,

262
00:17:10,177 --> 00:17:14,352
but then it really did take you that long to fall in love with me.

263
00:17:15,110 --> 00:17:18,177
You only came back a few months ago.

264
00:17:18,177 --> 00:17:21,552
It's not possible for you to have already fallen in love with someone.

265
00:17:22,502 --> 00:17:26,152
Plus, I know you love me.

266
00:17:37,360 --> 00:17:38,985
Xinyi, I...

267
00:17:38,985 --> 00:17:40,778
Am I wrong?

268
00:17:40,778 --> 00:17:42,902
Alright, that's enough.

269
00:17:42,902 --> 00:17:44,460
I'm hungry.

270
00:17:44,460 --> 00:17:46,460
Why aren't the dishes being served yet?

271
00:17:47,402 --> 00:17:49,436
I'm going to the washroom.

272
00:18:03,940 --> 00:18:07,320
<i>[ZX]</i>

273
00:18:46,294 --> 00:18:48,459
There you are.

274
00:18:50,527 --> 00:18:51,959
Piggy.

275
00:18:52,927 --> 00:18:54,678
Here to see me?

276
00:18:55,235 --> 00:18:57,052
I'm so curious.

277
00:18:57,052 --> 00:18:58,427
Come on.

278
00:19:12,736 --> 00:19:14,169
Sihan.

279
00:19:15,527 --> 00:19:17,277
Let me introduce you.

280
00:19:17,277 --> 00:19:19,611
She is my best friend,

281
00:19:19,611 --> 00:19:20,969
Zhang Xiao.

282
00:19:20,969 --> 00:19:25,702
This is who couldn't make it yesterday, Mr. Kang Sihan.

283
00:19:29,736 --> 00:19:31,260
