Shouldn't you give me a reward?

556
00:38:17,219 --> 00:38:19,778
I think you should ask your mother for a reward.

557
00:38:19,778 --> 00:38:21,859
She's your boss after all.

558
00:38:21,859 --> 00:38:25,427
My boss seems to like you.

559
00:38:25,427 --> 00:38:30,119
She told me to invite you over for dinner.

560
00:38:32,152 --> 00:38:35,443
Why did you call me this morning by the way?

561
00:38:37,444 --> 00:38:39,752
It's nothing important.

562
00:38:55,719 --> 00:38:57,386
Piggy.

563
00:38:58,235 --> 00:39:00,194
Princess.

564
00:39:00,194 --> 00:39:01,819
What a coincidence.

565
00:39:01,819 --> 00:39:04,194
Yeah, did you come visit your boyfriend?

566
00:39:04,194 --> 00:39:06,819
No, I came for a meeting.

567
00:39:06,819 --> 00:39:08,402
Why are you here?

568
00:39:08,402 --> 00:39:09,859
I work here.

569
00:39:09,859 --> 00:39:11,778
I just started recently.

570
00:39:11,778 --> 00:39:12,960
Sihan.

571
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:14,586
You work together.

572
00:39:14,586 --> 00:39:17,010
You never met before?

573
00:39:17,010 --> 00:39:18,511
I...

574
00:39:18,511 --> 00:39:19,486
The company is so big.

575
00:39:19,486 --> 00:39:20,752
More than 3,000 people.

576
00:39:20,752 --> 00:39:22,552
We had no chance to meet.

577
00:39:23,302 --> 00:39:24,802
You're right.

578
00:39:26,519 --> 00:39:27,843
I'll get going now.

579
00:39:27,843 --> 00:39:29,094
Okay.

580
00:39:29,843 --> 00:39:32,902
Wait, what's that?

581
00:39:32,902 --> 00:39:34,027
Lunch.

582
00:39:34,027 --> 00:39:35,360
Why do you have so many?

583
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:38,319
Are they bullying you because you're new?

584
00:39:38,319 --> 00:39:40,860
No, I just happened to get it for them.

585
00:39:40,860 --> 00:39:42,469
Hi, Director Kang.

586
00:39:42,469 --> 00:39:44,110
Can you help me take this up?

587
00:39:44,110 --> 00:39:44,969
Sure.

588
00:39:44,969 --> 00:39:46,640
Thank you.

589
00:39:46,640 --> 00:39:47,960
See?

590
00:39:48,736 --> 00:39:51,177
Let's find your supervisor.

591
00:39:51,177 --> 00:39:52,527
- Xinyi.
- It's fine.

592
00:39:52,527 --> 00:39:53,694
Forget it.

593
00:39:53,694 --> 00:39:54,778
What?

594
00:39:54,778 --> 00:39:56,444
Don't make it bigger than it is.

595
00:39:56,444 --> 00:39:59,527
Sihan, listen.

596
00:39:59,527 --> 00:40:01,652
Zhang Xiao is my best friend.

597
00:40:01,652 --> 00:40:04,611
I won't forgive even you if she gets bullied.

598
00:40:04,611 --> 00:40:07,085
Please take care of my best friend.

599
00:40:07,085 --> 00:40:12,110
Besides, she's the woman I love the most, second only to my mother.

600
00:40:14,627 --> 00:40:16,360
Stop it.

601
00:40:16,360 --> 00:40:17,444
What?

602
00:40:17,444 --> 00:40:19,377
I'm telling it like it is.

603
00:40:19,377 --> 00:40:22,827
If this happens again, I will take down your entire company.

604
00:40:23,344 --> 00:40:27,069
Princess, stop it.

605
00:40:27,069 --> 00:40:29,819
Alright, let's go to lunch.

606
00:40:29,819 --> 00:40:32,736
I already bought lunch. Next time.

607
00:40:32,736 --> 00:40:34,127
Fine.

608
00:40:36,194 --> 00:40:37,759
I'm heading up now.

609
00:40:40,843 --> 00:40:42,386
Let's go.

610
00:40:49,527 --> 00:40:53,052
That's why I said Zhang Xiao...

611
00:40:56,152 --> 00:40:57,886
Zhang Xiao.

612
00:40:59,486 --> 00:41:00,902
I have some news.

613
00:41:00,902 --> 00:41:02,885
I don't know if I should tell you or not.

614
00:41:05,152 --> 00:41:09,527
Director Kang's real girlfriend is the daughter of Yin Feng Group.

615
00:41:09,527 --> 00:41:13,152
The news has been spreading amongst the higher-ups.

616
00:41:13,152 --> 00:41:15,694
You better watch out.

617
00:41:15,694 --> 00:41:17,802
A perfect match.

618
00:41:17,802 --> 00:41:19,694
They're the perfect example.

619
00:41:19,694 --> 00:41:23,544
Zhen Tian and Yin Feng is family now.

620
00:41:24,502 --> 00:41:26,135
What do you think?

621
00:41:32,569 --> 00:41:35,027
Zhang Xiao, are you alright?

622
00:41:35,027 --> 00:41:37,694
Zhang Xiao has it tough.

623
00:41:37,694 --> 00:41:39,427
But it can be a good thing.

624
00:41:39,427 --> 00:41:42,110
She can wake up now.

625
00:41:42,110 --> 00:41:46,527
You should know the difference between reality and a fairy tale.

626
00:41:46,527 --> 00:41:50,378
Not everyone can be Cinderella.

627
00:41:54,569 --> 00:41:55,869
Here.

628
00:41:57,135 --> 00:41:58,319
I told you.

629
00:41:58,319 --> 00:42:00,552
Men can't be trusted.

630
00:42:00,552 --> 00:42:02,069
Don't cry anymore.

631
00:42:02,069 --> 00:42:04,194
Don't let him take advantage of you.

632
00:42:04,194 --> 00:42:06,510
Our time is valuable.

633
00:42:06,510 --> 00:42:07,760
You should ask him for stuff.

634
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:11,110
At least some compensation.

635
00:42:11,110 --> 00:42:13,886
This amount.

636
00:42:15,277 --> 00:42:19,219
No, this amount.

637
00:42:40,594 --> 00:42:46,885
♫ <i>Time passes quickly, so love in the moment</i> ♫

638
00:42:46,885 --> 00:42:54,836
♫ <i>Would rather be hurt than to feel empty</i> ♫

639
00:42:54,836 --> 00:42:58,027
♫ <i>Everyone wants to be loved, looking for a future</i> ♫

640
00:42:58,027 --> 00:43:00,102
Why isn't the car here yet?

641
00:43:05,860 --> 00:43:09,778
Lao Li, where are you?

642
00:43:09,778 --> 00:43:12,135
I've decided.

643
00:43:12,135 --> 00:43:13,894
Let's break up.

644
00:43:15,302 --> 00:43:16,544
Xiaoxiao, don't do this.

645
00:43:16,544 --> 00:43:17,927
Calm down.

646
00:43:17,927 --> 00:43:19,943
I am sorry.

647
00:43:19,943 --> 00:43:23,527
I'm sorry for making you uncomfortable with this decision.

648
00:43:23,527 --> 00:43:27,586
I'm not uncomfortable. I feel guilty.

649
00:43:27,586 --> 00:43:29,960
Don't do this.

650
00:43:29,960 --> 00:43:31,827
Remember.

651
00:43:32,360 --> 00:43:35,902
Zhang Xiao was with Black Cat Detective.

652
00:43:35,902 --> 00:43:38,235
Not Kang Sihan.

653
00:43:38,235 --> 00:43:41,360
Now Black Cat Detective no longer exists.

654
00:43:41,360 --> 00:43:44,836
Kang Sihan has nothing to feel sorry for.

655
00:43:47,360 --> 00:43:48,759
Also,

656
00:43:49,819 --> 00:43:52,878
rumors are spreading throughout the company.

657
00:43:53,819 --> 00:43:57,394
Don't let Xinyi hear any of it.

658
00:43:57,969 --> 00:44:00,860
Xinyi is a simple and innocent girl.

659
00:44:00,860 --> 00:44:02,927
Treat her well.

660
00:44:05,960 --> 00:44:08,710
Or I won't forgive you.

661
00:44:11,760 --> 00:44:13,100
Hello?

662
00:44:53,719 --> 00:44:55,110
What are you doing?

663
00:44:55,860 --> 00:44:57,859
Let go of me.

664
00:44:57,859 --> 00:44:59,244
Don't move.
